hopobject.body: I'd like to take the job tagsupplements.tradeindia.com Katy Perry's getting naked again. What's her excuse this time? It's for art, people!The 25-year-old singer proved her upcoming album's title, 'Teenage Dream,' correct when she unveiled the saucy cover art by contemporary painter Will Cotton during a live chat on Ustream. The artist - who also acted as artistic director on Perry's candy-coated 'California Gurls' video - offers up the brunette babe hugging a cotton-candy pink cloud as she lies on her stomach, a strip of the sweet treat covering her rear end.
